Subject: Substitute FI Fuel Pump #

Hi Volks,

A fuel-pump thread on the Vanagon list has uncovered a VERY useful 
tidbit of information for those with fuel injected buses. The original 
VW pump is not commonly stocked at a FLAPS and is usually priced near 
$200US when you can fin one. We now identified a source for affordable 
replacement fuel pumps... The NAPA part # is 2P74028.

Many thanks to Charles Hill for supplying this part number.

Happy trails,

Greg Potts
Toronto, Ontario, Canada

